headline: 2 Dividend Stocks to Hold for the Next 2 Years
summary: Dividend stocks can generate reliable passive income.  The key is to find companies that have a strong track record of paying and increasing their dividends.  Investors also want to be sure that they are picking companies that can generate enough earnings and free cash flow to cover and raise their dividends in the future.
